## Limitations
The analysis is limited by the availability of up-to-date sources and the potential bias in the selected materials. Some sources may present a one-sided view, either overly positive or negative, regarding the role of pressure groups in democracy. Additionally, the focus on UK and US contexts may not fully capture the global perspective on the issue. Further research could include a broader range of geographical contexts and more recent data to provide a more comprehensive understanding.